this fall. ...</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Aparna Chennapragada, Robinh=
ood=E2=80=99s product chief, said that the marketing push is a continuation=
 of Robinhood=E2=80=99s long-term mission to make investing accessible to p=
eople who hadn=E2=80=99t historically participated in the markets. The camp=
aign, she said, is about =E2=80=9Cmeeting the next generation where they ar=
e=E2=80=9D and communicating that by starting young, college students can e=
njoy the benefits of compound returns over decades.</p><p style=3D"margin: =
16px 0;">Courting students is tricky for Robinhood. Critics say the app has=
 turned trading into a game-like experience that encourages unsophisticated=
 investors to take risks they don=E2=80=99t understand.</p></blockquote><p =
style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yes, if you are 18 and you buy weekly-expiry out-=
of-the-money call options on GameStop Corp. every week from now until you r=
etire you will definitely compound at a rate of =E2=80=A6 no honestly I can=
