off by day-trading Dogecoin and YOLOing weekly GameStop options.[6] It is a=
n inexpensive and=C2=A0appropriately timed<em>=C2=A0</em>form of investor e=
ducation: Better to do your wild day-trading=C2=A0with a tiny account in co=
llege, get burned, get it out of your system, and then have 40 sadder and w=
iser years to save for retirement. The way to become a sophisticated invest=
or taking risks that you do understand is mostly to start as an unsophistic=
ated investor, take risks you don=E2=80=99t understand, lose money and lear=
